  "texts": [
    "We use the sparse routing control with the lightweight finetuning method LoRA to activate different experts, aiming to reduce computational costs.",
    "Fig. 2.2Fig.",
    "Overview of Uni-MoE Training Methodology.",
    "The progressive training stages contain: 1) Utilize pairs from different modalities and languages to train connectors that map these elements to a unified language space, establishing a foundation for multimodal understanding; 2) Develop modality-specific experts using cross-modal data to ensure deep understanding, preparing for a cohesive multi-expert model; 3) Incorporate multiple trained experts into LLMs and refine the unified multimodal model using the LoRA technique on mixed multimodal data.",
    "Fig. 3.3Fig."
